# - `private_extensions/ugc_file_tools` 已对外；但 `private_extensions/**/out/**` 等仍为本地产物，保持忽略。
# - Level/关卡专项内容生产脚本（如“第七关/亲戚”）属于项目数据生产链，不作为通用工具对外发布。
tools/ui_workbench_batch_export_bundle_and_patch_gil.py
tools/diagnose_equal_string_constants.py
tools/generate_min_ui_node9_fixture.py
tools/scan_ugc_file_tools_import_policy.py
tools/extract_gia_template_names_for_graphs.py
tools/inspect_gil_id_ref.py
tools/fix_import_policy_*.py
tools/debug_ui_workbench_*.py
tools/generate_level7_*.py
tools/import_level7_*.py
tools/naturalize_level7_*.py
tools/patch_level7_*.py



